ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend this to any student with a serious interest in developing Monte Carlo simulations or writing their own statistical code. This applied to students in not just Economics, but its cognate fields and Statistics.
A must for students interested in quantitative models in economics.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The course exposed me to the necessary tools to do state of the art computational methods.
Should be a semester long with homeworks. This way professor and students would take it more seriously.
